@backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5241

### Get all bands
GET {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/bands
Accept: application/json

### Get band by id (replace {{id}} or set env variable)
# GET {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/bands/{{id}}
# Accept: application/json

### Create a band
POST {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/bands
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "The Rolling Codes",
  "genre": "Rock",
  "dateTime": "2025-11-09T20:00:00Z",
  "stage": "Main"
}

